originalText.text: My husband and I had amazing experience shooting our wedding photos with Nazar. Truly an amazing photographer and a great person to work with. Nazar took out the time to completely get an understanding of the type of photos I wanted and I was totally impressed with how they turned out. They exceeded my expectations and we are truly in love with our wedding photos. I can not recommend Nazar enough, he was a pleasure to work with and I look forward to shooting more in the future with him!
